<div id="post-439611" class="blog-post position-8 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/branco/blog/via-rsurgente-ameacas-que-pairam-sobre-a-liberdade-na-internet-no-brasil">Via @RSUrgente: Ameaças que pairam sobre a liberdade na internet no Brasil</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">5 de Junho de 2012, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"></span></span><div class="short-post"><h1 class="entry-title" style="font-size: 2.2em; margin-bottom: 0px; border-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; font-family: 'trebuchet MS', verdana, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1; color: #111111; text-align: left; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px;">Marcelo Branco aponta ameaças que pairam sobre a liberdade na internet no Brasil</h1>
<div class="entry-byline" style="border-color: initial; font-size: 1.1em; vertical-align: baseline; color: #777777; font-family: 'trebuchet ms', sans-serif; font-style: italic; text-align: left; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">
<span class="entry-date" style="border-color: initial; font-size: 11px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><abbr class="updated" title="2012-06-04T21:10:14+0000" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Jun 4th, 2012</abbr></span> <address class="author vcard" style="border-color: initial; font-size: 11px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">by <a href="http://rsurgente.opsblog.org/2012/06/04/marcelo-branco-aponta-ameacas-que-pairam-sobre-a-liberdade-na-internet-no-brasil/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rsurgente+%28RS+URGENTE%29" title="rs urgente" target="_blank" style="border-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: #777777; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Marco Aurélio Weissheimer</a>.</address>
